<br><br>
Regardless of which term is used, statutory and mandatory training ensures that all staff members have the knowledge to maintain a healthy and safe working environment for themselves and their colleagues.</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-fUklNj thmnJ pf-156_ pf-heading-1-h3 _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-158_">Conclusion - The differences between mandatory and statutory training
